1.content:
Tommy just got a novel that has something to do with tickling. He went home and read the first chapter. "So I have to sneak up on my friends huh?" Tommy said to himself. Tommy and his friends were hanging out at the Java Lava. "I can do this." Tommy thought. And then, he sneaked up on his friend Chuckie and tickled him. Chuckie didn't expect the surprise but he laughed anyway. After that, Tommy tickled Kimi. She was extremely ticklish that she laughed out loud. After that, Tommy tickled Phil and Lil. They laughed hard. And then Tommy tickled Susie. She laughed too.

When Tommy was done tickling his friends, he left. His friends were talking about his new tickle fetish and decided to get him!
1.title: All Grown Up Tickling: Tommy's Novel

11.content:
Tommy was in the middle of a good chapter right after he tickled his own brother Dil. His friends were at the front of his house. "Let's get him!" Kimi yelled. Everybody else agreed. They went in his house and barged in his room. "Hey guys, what are you doing here?" Tommy asked. His friends didn't answer him. "Is he ticklish?" Kimi asked Chuckie. Chuckie nodded. He even remembered that Tommy has been ticklish cause they tickled each other when they were younger and even now. Phil and Lil tied him up to his bed with some rope they had. Kimi and Chuckie grabbed feathers out of their pockets. Phil and Lil grabbed toothbrushes, even Susie did as well.

Suddenly, Angelica barged in the room. "So I heard you guys are tickling Tommy." She said, "Can I join you?" Everyone nodded their heads except for Tommy. Phil and Lil started tickling Tommy's armpits, Angelica tickled his tummy, Susie tickled his side, and Kimi and Chuckie started tickling his feet. Dil was even tickling Tommy's other side. Tommy was laughing so hard because he was very ticklish. He didn't like his friends doing it, especially Angelica. He begged and pleaded to stop.

So what's gonna happen next?
11.title: Friends Get Tommy

111.content:
So his friends kept tickling him. It has been an hour since he has been tickled. Tommy's cheeks turned pink from the long tickling. He tried to break free of his restraints but he couldn't. Angelica made sure he was pinned.

Tommy's friends tickled him until they grew bored. "Let's go to the Java Lava." Kimi said, "I'm thirsty from all that tickling." Then everybody else agreed. They left Tommy there all tied up. He actually passed out from the heavy torture!

He woke up a few hours later. It was dark outside. "Guys, guys, a little help here." Tommy said. Dil came in and untied him. Before you knew it, Dil and Tommy were having a huge tickle fight until they collapsed. They then said goodnight to each other. And Tommy fell into a deep sleep.

THE END!
111.title: Keep tickling him!

1111.content:
Johnny Test wasn't just an ordinary kid. He was always tested by his twin sisters Mary and Susan. His talking dog Dukey was always with him. Those two were best buds. It wasn't any ordinary day at all. Mary and Susan were performing experiments on Johnny and Dukey was watching him and laughing. Suddenly, an unknown person kidnapped all of them by gagging them until they passed out.

What's gonna happen next?
1111.title: Johnny Test Tickling

11111.content: The mysterious person turned out to be the Tickler! He was back! (From the episode Johnny vs. The Tickler)! Yes, the Tickler was back for revenge! "You!" Johnny yelled. "Yes, it is me, the Tickler!" He said. "What do you want from us?" Mary asked. "Revenge you silly girl!" The Tickler said. He then pushed a red button. Johnny, Mary, Susan and Dukey were tied up. Feathers were tickling all of them all over their bodies. They were giggling and laughing cause it tickled so bad!
11111.title: It's the Tickler!

111111.content:
Johnny Test, Dukey, Mary and Susan were still tickle tortured. The Tickler laughed evilly at their torture. They all begged for it to stop but to no avail.

They called for help and still nothing. But someone will come to their rescue. But who?
111111.title: They're Tickle Tortured!

1111111.content:
Their parents come to their rescue! But the Tickler traps them and tickle tortures them along with Johnny, Dukey, Mary and Susan!

Who can save them now?
1111111.title: Their Parents

11111111.content:
Sooo, a surprise happens! That's when I made the scene! I just barged right in there. I had to save them even if I wasn't a big fan of Johnny Test, (don't worry, I made the story anyway so people can be happy). "You let them go Tickler!" I yelled. "You won't be saving anyone! Maybe this will teach you a lesson!" The Tickler yelled. Then he pushed a red button and arms held me above my head and other arms started tickling my armpits, sides and stomach. I laughed and laughed cause I am extremely ticklish! But I am a strong girl cause I broke free after a few minutes.

Then I stopped the tickling for the poor kids and let them go. "Come on guys, let's get out of here." I said. I motioned them to run with me. "Oh no you don't!" The Tickler yelled. He ran after us. "Come on," I said. We ran faster.

Suddenly, I had a weapon! I shot it at the Tickler making him laugh so hard. "What is that weapon?" Johnny asked me. "Oh just a giggle gun I invented." I said, "It just tickles you but it eventually wears off." Then we ran faster arriving at their house. We stopped there to catch our breaths for a while.
11111111.title: Anyone?

111111111.content:
"So what's your name? You're our new hero." Johnny asked. "Oh my name's Lauren. And it was nothing, even if I'm not a big fan of you, I had to save you guys anyway." I explained. "You should be in our show." Dukey said. Then they agreed and patted my head. "Sorry guys, I can't. I'm not a fan of this show remember?" I said. Then I disappeared surprisingly.

Johnny, Mary, Susan and Dukey just stood there thinking about what just happened.


THE END!
111111111.title: A Promotion!

1111111111.content:
There was a 12 year old girl named Alania. She was a weird girl in every way. She has been obsessed with a 15 year old boy named Zach for a long time. Right now she was watching his every move. "I wish I could have his body." Alania said, "He just looks so hot."

And then, something happened.
1111111111.title: A Body Stealing Girl!

11111111111.content:
Alania permanently stole Zach's body. She is now in his body and Zach is in Alania's body. There was no way the swap can change. Things were going to stay like this forever. Alania got her wish. Now she can do things that she has always wanted to do.

What will she do?
11111111111.title: Body swap!

111111111111.content:
Alania did her makeup and did the part of her short hair a lot. Now her boyish body is a girl. When Zach, (in Alania's body) saw her, he freaked out. Alania smiled wickedly at Zach. She pounced on what used to be her body and kissed Zach. Zach screamed in horror. "Oh this is great! I love being in Zach's body!" She said to herself.

Zach didn't like this at all. He wanted to be back in his own body but there is nothing that can be done. They both are in those bodies permanently, so they will just have to make the best of things...for now.
111111111111.title: Girly things

15111.content:
One morning, Didi Pickles was checking the mail, when she got a letter.

It was written in all caps: IMPORTANT! ALL LEGAL GUARDIANS OF INFANTS UNDER TWO YEARS OLD IN THE USA MUST REPORT TO LIPSCHITZ'S INFANT LABORATORY AND BRING THEIR CHILDREN WITHIN THE NEXT FIVE MONTHS. THEY ARE REQUIRED FOR TESTING."

Didi then showed Stu the letter.

"I suppose we'll have to make the trip sooner or later, so how about today?" asked Stu.

They then drove off to Lipschitz's lab and sat in the waiting room.

In the waiting room were several parents of babies, including Betty and Howard, who'd brought along Phil and Lil, and the boy Hector and his parents, who Tommy had met when he got given his booster shot.

First, the DeVilles got called in, and after what felt like a really long time, they came back.
"How did the test go?" asked Didi.
"Fine, Deed," said Betty, "but the doc said not to worry if the pups develop superpowers. Pretty sure he was just kidding, but it would be pretty radical to have two superhero pups."

"Wow," said Tommy to the twins, "you might get superpowers."
"Yeah, 'parently", said Phil, "but I that if we do, mine will be better than yours, Lillian."
"Will not, Philip!" said Lil angrily and the twins began to argue.

When the Pickleses were called in, they handed Tommy and Dil over to Lipschitz's assistant, who fed them a strange potion.

After they drank it, Dil seemed normal, but Tommy started to change.
"Deed! He's turning blue!" said Stue.

And he was, his whole face was becoming dark blue.
"Tommy?!" said Didi in a very fearful voice.
"Sorry, Mrs Pickles," said Lipschitz, "I have been given reports of the experiment giving infants powers, but never effects like this!".
Soon, the whole of Tommy's body was dark blue, and then he started to swell up.

"Help!" said Didi.

When Tommy had stopped swelling, he was about the size of a very large beanbag chair.

What happens now?
15111.title: A requirement experimental test for babies
